data.description: LIKE LIVING IN A TREE HOUSE. . .  This reverse plan home is perfect blend of a usable lot, remodeled home, and a stunning roof top patio for entertaining, even projecting movies! Enter the Zen Garden, to the wrap around front patio. It features an updated kitchen with white shaker cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and large basin, under mount sink. Natural light floods through the windows as you peer onto the rooftop patio. Imagine entertaining your friends, enjoying your morning coffee or gazing at the stars. The master has outdoor access, dual sinks, cherry cabinetry and tile flooring in the bathroom. Newer whole house fan for those warm summer days. Home is located in Lake Wildwood a gated community that provides residents a stunning private lake spanning over 300 acres for almost all your favorite water activities. An array of amenities that cater to an active and vibrant lifestyle. Residents have access to a Golf Course, Tennis Courts, Pickle Ball, Pool, Trails and well-maintained Parks. Enjoy Club House Dining.
